cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper proposes a data-driven online video stabilization method using deep learning, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The method involves processing each frame in a multi-scale manner, which could also be categorized under multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves synthesizing unstable videos, which could be categorized under graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
